{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2289517, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "劝君少骂秦始皇", "timestamp": 1629088915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "秦王扫六合", "timestamp": 1629088925, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289526, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哪怕是统一的民族认同，也是因为有东西汉400年的长期稳定统治吧", "timestamp": 1629088963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "真的少骂，这是开创观念", "timestamp": 1629089071, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289547, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "秦始皇您的国民辛苦劳作，但愿他们的手上永远没有水泡。", "timestamp": 1629089099, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289565, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289526, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没有始皇帝的统一，也会有后面的统一，有人担统一的美誉，就有人认为其要担上统一的骂名。另外始皇帝被骂也不是因为统一啊，不是因为暴政吗。人家统一也是靠自己的实力啊，那么多秦王努力了那么多代", "timestamp": 1629089182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289567, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "去看看毛主席评价秦始皇的一首诗你就明白秦始皇的伟大了", "timestamp": 1629089204, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289526, "tag": null, "text": "秦始皇的功远大于过", "timestamp": 1629089233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289539, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不是我骂啊，是大家都骂了几千年了，这十年突然翻案了捧成千古一帝了", "timestamp": 1629089247, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289577, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "秦始皇统一奠定中华民族的根基。印度到现在还没有统一民族认同只能用宗教取最大公因数", "timestamp": 1629089283, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289570, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我并不想评价始皇的功过，我只是好奇舆论突然反转背后的原因", "timestamp": 1629089307, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289588, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "革命的时候就要树靶子，还管什么矫枉过正", "timestamp": 1629089349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289592, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289572, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你只是读书少\n《三国志•魏纪二》\n（曹叡）为太子时，不与大臣交结，即位之初，侍中刘晔独被召见，出则谓群臣言：“秦始皇，汉武帝之俦，才具微不及耳。”", "timestamp": 1629089385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289592, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 你这都只是个例，两千年来哪怕就是十年前对始皇的评价绝对是负面的远多于正面的，但就是近几年突然就万人颂扬千古一帝了", "timestamp": 1629089498, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“我记得”", "timestamp": 1629089528, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "什么罗马势力", "timestamp": 1629089538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289611, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289547, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 秦始皇！您的国民是您最强大的力量！好好保护您的国民，您将名垂千古！", "timestamp": 1629089547, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289583, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 被骂几千年难道不是因为秦始皇是一个二世而亡的经典例子，历朝历代劝君防止暴政亡国当然要举这个例子。看的角度不一样有什么问题吗，封建体制下最关注的当然是防止亡国灭朝。而且，名声不好也只会是这个角度，至于其他角度，也没见你举出论据啊", "timestamp": 1629089711, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289603, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我跟你说一万个你也只能说是个例，你要是读完了两千年的二十四史，看看优秀的政治家、改革家、历史学家怎么评价秦始皇，再来说绝对不绝对。两千年来人们还觉得天圆地方，太阳绕着地球转。", "timestamp": 1629089733, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "秦始皇评价反转绝不是近几年，看看毛主席的评价吧", "timestamp": 1629089787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289688, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "即使是大家最为熟知的《过秦论》。仔细读读就知道了，也不乏对始皇帝和其先辈历代秦王励精图治统一天下的赞美。虽然是欲抑先扬，但是评价很客观的", "timestamp": 1629090134, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289703, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "无关话题，只是想想，欧洲几千年来也不缺大帝国，短暂几个世代就碎成一地。那样倒不会有什么始皇帝的说法。", "timestamp": 1629090235, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289577, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是印度这次的金牌得主回国的时候也被热烈欢迎了，感觉国家认同感还是有的呀", "timestamp": 1629090342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289723, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289632, "tag": null, "text": "始皇帝是中华的根基历朝历代承认始皇帝就是一种政权合法性", "timestamp": 1629090386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289738, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz想说的是“风评”、“风向”的那种“感觉”对吧，就好像2011、12年的时候社会舆论中的美国还是令人向往的灯塔国形象，现在就“下凡”成了虽先进但也丑恶的国家hhh甚至香港对内地人的吸引力也连带着下降\ncz很难说风向是怎么操纵的，但也确实感觉到了dz所描述的现象hhh", "timestamp": 1629090455, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289744, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289717, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 印度内部矛盾很大的呀邦与邦之间", "timestamp": 1629090478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这就跟计划生育相关的风向一样  跟着上面吹呗hh", "timestamp": 1629090524, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289844, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以前强调的是秦皇汉武好大喜功，虚耗民力的一面，目的在于借古讽今教育当权者爱惜民力；现在要塑造民族认同了，自然是要强调其一扫六合，屏退强虏的功绩了。", "timestamp": 1629091202, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2289935, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289752, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 这有什么可类比的吗？秦始皇自建国以来的评价一直如此，哪有什么近十年突然翻转", "timestamp": 1629091931, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2290043, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你不看看后面儒学当道，肯定骂秦始皇是政治正确啊", "timestamp": 1629092882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2290807, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289935, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: Kate是哪一年上初中，学到中国古代史的？", "timestamp": 1629100410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2290829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2289935, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 没有别的意思，就是想问问", "timestamp": 1629100550, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2291783, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2290807, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 课本有什么重大的变化吗", "timestamp": 1629107904, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2291813, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2290807, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 我国官方从来都是唯物史观评价的，肯定其建立统一的多民族国家的贡献，也指出其暴力剥削压迫人民的事实。功过分开", "timestamp": 1629108241, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2292092, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 439984, "reply_to": 2291813, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 七三开", "timestamp": 1629111006, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 13, "pid": 439984, "reply": 35, "tag": null, "text": "秦始皇是因为近十年需要强调统一和民族团结才翻案成\"千古一帝\"的吗，我记得几千年来他的名声可一直不怎么好", "timestamp": 1629088829, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629111007, "url": "", "vote": {}}}